Introduction

Chunseo is a Spanish-Filipino singer and rapper under FrontRow Records. She is a member and the maknae of London-based girl group ATTI and formerly KAACHI. Prior to joining KAACHI, Chunseo was a member of the London-based K-pop dance cover group, UJJN, along with fellow KAACHI members Nicole and Dani.
